The purpose of this study is to support licensure of GSK Biologicals' MMR vaccine (Priorix(R)) in the US by generating immunogenicity and safety data in contrast to the US standard of care, Merck's MMR vaccine (M-M-R(R)II), when given as a second dose to children four to six years of age.

